{"about_the_game":"<br><br>In Vandalhalla you play to bring back amusement in a near future where fun is forbidden.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/fun_2.png?t=1636052542\" /><br><br>You will bring back the fun in the city by participating in illegal fights. This fights highly recommends you to destroy the environment, kill your opponents and control capture points.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/wip2_steam.gif?t=1636052542\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/arsenal_2.png?t=1636052542\" /><br><br>Vandalhalla give you a large panel of short, medium and long ranged weapons, grenades and diverse mechanics. Numerous classic and original abilities for always more interesting and chaotic battles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/wip.gif?t=1636052542\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/freedom.png?t=1636052542\" /><br><br>When you enter a battle you need to compose first a loadout with some weapons and abilities of the arsenal, then you are free.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/loadout.gif?t=1636052542\" /><br><br>Free to steal doors from building and killing opponents with it.<br>Free to catch missiles and send it back to the sender.<br>Free to become the weapon and throw yourself in a kamikaze style.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/physics_2.png?t=1636052542\" /><br><br>Physical interaction is the key in Vandalhalla as you can see above, you can do whatever you with the help of your Gravi